; Coverage for filters.cc
; rewrite_posts::operator() with account-rewrite directive.
; When the account rewrite matches, it creates a temp post and copies
; account xdata flags from the previous account.

account-rewrite  Expenses:Food  Expenses:Groceries

2024/01/01 Grocery
    Expenses:Food    $25.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg
24-Jan-01 Grocery               Expenses:Groceries           $25.00       $25.00
24-Jan-01 Grocery               Assets:Cash                 $-25.00            0
end test
